name: Pure White Sugar
description:
This is on a ladies Gildan soft style cotton tee with gold ink.

As an observation at a cafe.  The waitress brought a tea and a coffee, I asked for sugar. A second waitress came over with white sugar and brown hair. My friend asked if there was any brown sugar in town.  A third waitress arrived with the brown sugar and blond hair.  When asked where she came from she said the kitchen.

In the end I put salt in my coffee, brown sauce in the tea and vinegar on the dog.  To solve this misunderstanding these sugar vests should do the trick.

Next problem was the vet to get my grannies dog off my leg.

name: Little Pecker
description:
This is on a ladies Fruit of the Loom organic cotton tee in natural off white colour.

Printed with plastisol ink and a finesse base for a soft feel in three colours.

A word of warning, don't ever go up to my grannies parrot and say coochie coochie cock-a-doodle-doo while eating a chocolate biscuit.
